        </article>

        <article class="testim-card">
          <div class="testim-avatar testim-avatar-2"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img=39" alt="Priscilla M., senior VP relocating to Florida" width="300" height="300" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/300x300/F0EDE8/6B5C4B/png?text=39';"></div>
          <blockquote class="testim-quote">"I was relocating from Connecticut with a sign-on bonus, a forgivable-note retention package, and a relocation gross-up. Two lenders said the package was too complex to underwrite. Jim ran it cleanly. We closed before my start date."</blockquote>
          <div class="testim-attribution">
            <div class="testim-name">Priscilla M.</div>
            <div class="testim-meta">Senior VP &middot; Tech company &middot; Boca Raton</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="testim-card">
          <div class="testim-avatar testim-avatar-3"><img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img=40" alt="Raj P., pre-IPO director at a hot startup" width="300" height="300" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/300x300/E8EFE8/3D5A3D/png?text=40';"></div>
          <blockquote class="testim-quote">"I had $3.8M of unvested ISOs that the lender said didn&rsquo;t count. We waited until after the secondary tender, used the proceeds plus asset-depletion on the remaining vested shares. Approved at the right number, closed before year-end."</blockquote>
          <div class="testim-attribution">
            <div class="testim-name">Raj P.</div>
